	"description"		"[h1]Enlisted - Military Service Mod[/h1]

[i]Enlist with any lord. Follow orders. Climb the ranks. Retire with honor.[/i]

Transform Bannerlord from a conquest simulator into a deep soldier career experience. Instead of managing an empire, you serve one. Features [b]245 narrative content pieces[/b] spanning [b]9 military ranks[/b] from fresh recruit to senior commander.

[h2]Key Features[/h2]
[list]
[*][b]9 Military Ranks:[/b] Progress from recruit to marshal with culture-specific titles (Empire, Vlandia, Sturgia, Khuzait, Battania, Aserai)
[*][b]Multi-Factor Promotions:[/b] XP, service time, battles fought, reputation, and discipline all matter
[*][b]Chain of Command:[/b] 16 military orders with 85 dynamic events during duty execution
[*][b]Pay & Muster System:[/b] 12-day pay cycles with ceremonial payouts, performance bonuses, and tension mechanics
[*][b]Quartermaster System:[/b] 6 equipment quality tiers with upgrades and reputation-based discounts
[*][b]Camp Life Simulation:[/b] 33 player decisions, fatigue system, medical care, background events
[*][b]Commander's Retinue:[/b] Lead 20-40 hand-picked troops at senior ranks (T7-T9) with narrative events
[*][b]Identity & Reputation:[/b] Three reputation tracks (Lord, Officer, Soldier) and emergent specialization through traits
[*][b]Grace Period System:[/b] 14 days to transfer service if your lord dies or is captured
[*][b]Reservist Benefits:[/b] Re-enlist with same faction for tier bonuses and reputation restoration
[*][b]Optional Battle AI:[/b] Enhanced tactical decisions (disable anytime in launcher, field battles only)
[/list]

