When the changelog says CLEAN INSTALL RECOMMENDED, follow these steps:
[list=1]
[*]Unsubscribe from Enlisted in Steam Workshop
[*]Navigate to: [i]C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\workshop\content\261550\[/i]
[*]Delete the [b]3621116083[/b] folder
